            "text": "<p></p><p>By subscribing to the Mystery Tackle Box SMS program, you consent to receive recurring marketing and/or transactional messages from Mystery Tackle Box at the phone number provided. These messages may include cart reminders, promotions, account updates, order alerts, and other service notifications. Message frequency varies depending on your interactions with the program. Message and data rates may apply. SMS consent is not a condition of purchase. Texts may be sent using an automatic telephone dialing system.</p>",
