          "type": "section",
          "settings": {
            "section_id": "",
            "header": "<strong>How to Opt-In and Opt-Out</strong>",
            "text": "<p>To subscribe, text JOIN to 888-970-4682.</p><p>For help, text HELP to 888-970-4682, email <a href=\"mailto:support@mysterytacklebox.com\" title=\"mailto:support@mysterytacklebox.com\">support@mysterytacklebox.com</a></p><p>To unsubscribe, text STOP to 888-970-4682. You will receive a confirmation message, and no further messages will be sent unless you opt back in.</p><p></p>",
