            "text": "<p>This service is available to persons with text-capable phones subscribing to participating carriers, including, but not limited to, AT&T, Verizon Wireless, T-Mobile®, Sprint, Virgin Mobile USA, Cincinnati Bell, Centennial Wireless, Unicel, U.S. Cellular®, and Boost. Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.</p>",
